label.phrase: this sort of person behaves among other people as a surgeon does in the wards of a hospital his soul is really in his knife and the essence of these people lies in their fanatical faith in the surgeon's knife the surgeon's knife-that is the great theoretician the archphilosopher of the twentieth century
